<template>
    <v-container fluid class="fill-height">
      <v-row align="center" justify="center">
        <v-col cols="12" sm="8" md="6" lg="5" xl="4">
          <v-card>
            <v-toolbar dark color="blue-darken-4">
              <v-toolbar-title>Inicio de sesión</v-toolbar-title>
            </v-toolbar>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-text-field
                color="primary"
                label="Usuario"
                variant="underlined"
                required
              ></v-text-field>
              <v-text-field
                color="primary"
                label="Contraseña"
                variant="underlined"
                required
              ></v-text-field>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-card-actions class="px-3 pb-3">
              <v-spacer></v-spacer>
              <v-btn  color="primary" elevation="4">Ingresar</v-btn>
            </v-card-actions>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </template>
